            <category>
                <![CDATA[八達通]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1195684</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple iPhone 15 系列已陸續開始出貨，相信不少朋友也換了新機。iOS 系統要將資料轉移到新手機上非常方便，無論數據、信用卡等都可以輕易轉移到新電話上面。但坊間一直流傳 iOS 轉換資料時八達通轉至新 iPhone 時會出問題，身邊更有朋友試過登記了以八達通領取消費券，但因為未轉換八達通就賣了舊電話，又沒有紀錄自己的八達通卡號碼， 2000 元消費券就石沉大海。要避免八達通轉到新機時出現問題，可以按照以下介紹的方式去做，這個方法連 Apple 店員都會同顧客介紹，可説是目前最安全轉八達通到新機的方法。</p><p>要留意轉換過程中舊機和新機均需要保持互聯網連接（不論 Wi-Fi 或流動數據都 OK），以確保流程暢順。</p><h2>Step 1 先記錄八達通卡號，以保安全</h2><p>先開啟舊機的「錢包」，選擇你的八達通卡，點擊右上角的「…」，再點擊「卡號」，紀錄低你的八達通卡號碼。這個步驟並非必要，但如果轉換時不幸出現問題，你可以用先前紀錄低的八達通卡號碼向八達通公司求助。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195802" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08880-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開啟「…」，點擊「卡號」</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-1280x853.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-768x512.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-5.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先紀錄低你的卡號，以備不時之需</p><h2>Step 2 在舊機移除八達通卡</h2><p>紀錄了八達通號碼後，先回到上一頁，再選擇「卡的詳細資料」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「卡的詳細資料」</p><h2>Step 3</h2><p>紀錄了八達通號碼後，先回到上一頁，再選擇「卡的詳細資料」，掃到最底再選擇「移除卡」，確保在舊機上移除卡。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08881-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「卡的詳細資料」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08884-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲掃到最底選擇「移除卡」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08886-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲現在可以看到，小編已經從舊電話中移除了剛才的黑色八達通</p><h2>4. 拿出新機轉換八達通</h2><p>從舊機移除了八達通後，現在就可以拿新機出來。請確保你的新機、舊機都以相同的 Apple ID 登入。開啟新機的「錢包」，點擊「加入」，選擇「之前的卡」，再選擇你要轉換到新機的卡。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08888.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在新機上選擇「卡的詳細資料」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195821" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08890.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「之前的卡」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195824" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1-267x580.png" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1-267x580.png 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1-415x900.png 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/22-1.png 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇你要轉換的卡，小編就選擇了黑色八達通</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08907.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲轉換時新舊電話均需要連接互聯網</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195825" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08892.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果你的 iPhone 設有密碼，這時候就要輸入密碼</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08893.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲確認是你要轉移的八達通後，就可以按右上角的「下一步」</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08898.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看見此畫面就代表已完成轉換，正式可以在新機使用你原本的八達通卡</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1195829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/DSC08902.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲完成</p><h2>總結：使用上面方法轉換八達通就萬無一失</h2><p>如果按照上面步驟將八達通轉換至新 iPhone，就可以避免因無法控制的「技術問題」而整張八達通消失。即使不幸地在轉換過程中出了差池，也可憑藉八達通卡號碼向八達通公司求助。有些人可能選擇利用八達通領取消費券，假如遺失了的八達通既不是個人八達通卡，而且沒有紀錄低卡號碼的話，就會連消費券也石沈大海。</p><p>更安全而上面沒有提到的做法，是將八達通連結到你的八達通 App，但有些人不喜歡這樣做，主要是擔憂私隱問題，那要看各位自己的睇法。起碼上面提到的是最基本保護自己的方法。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
